@startuml
title PFD flow between Openness and 5G core

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam participantStyle rectangle
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor LightYellow
}
hide footbox

actor "Admin" as admin1 at leftmost
participant "<b>OpenNESS Controller Components</b>" as openess_controller #lightblue{
    partition "" {
        node UI/CLI 
        node Af Microservice  
    }

    box Get all transactions with PFD #white;#black;line.bold;text:green;font.size=20;;line.dashed;color:red;backgroundcolor:white;border.color:black:border.width:3px

    Admin ->UI/CLi : Request all PFD transactions\naf/v1/pfd/transaction GET \nOK:PFD information\ERROR 

     af microservic->NGC_STUB(UDR SMF):Request transactionId get pfd details via NEF using REST API call to retrieve data from NGCP function in order for us provide this service our customers who need access their own private networks or public ones like ours where they can use them without any restrictions imposed by other parties such governments etcetera... 

end box


@enduml
